code: @Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o) {         return true.     }     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass()) {         return false.     }     Event event = (Event) o.     return key == event.key && eventTime == event.eventTime && sequenceNumber == event.sequenceNumber && Objects.equals(payload, event.payload). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(key, eventTime, sequenceNumber, payload). }
@Override public String toString() {     return "Event{" + "key=" + key + ", eventTime=" + eventTime + ", sequenceNumber=" + sequenceNumber + ", payload='" + payload + '\'' + '}'. }
